{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>&quot;The ice age, Father's shop, and the Sunfire stone...&quot;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>An endless winter grips the world. With a long winter of unknown causes, many people die from hunger and cold. This disaster is called the 'Last Winter'. After receiving a letter, Will returns to his hometown of Arbyen. He takes over his father's shop and runs it in his absence.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666750/extras/STEAM_GIF_02.gif?t=1732736997\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>&quot;Farming : Survive from the Cold&quot;</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world has become too cold.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To get fuel and food, you have to go out and fight against the cold, snowstorms, and wild animals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666750/extras/STEAM_GIF_03.gif?t=1732736997\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>&quot;Management : Run your father's shop&quot;</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The store is a perfect place for enduring colder nights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We need to keep the furnace from going out, and the food from running out.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666750/extras/STEAM_GIF_05.gif?t=1732736997\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>&quot;Exploration : Chase the missing father and the Sunfire stone&quot;</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many resources and secrets hidden in the mining town of 'Arbyen'.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore more forests and underground areas, and follow the trail of father and the Sunfire stone.</p></li></ul><p cla